cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with image processing and computer vision techniques, specifically multi-focus image fusion using deep neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.MM (Machine Learning), and deep neural networks, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper proposes a new approach to dataset generation, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves analyzing and handling different situations, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics).
